r) and intensity of his austerities, the learned worshipped Brahma.\"","words":[{"d":"वरदानेन","m":"by the boon"},{"d":"बलिना","m":"mighty"},{"d":"रक्षसा","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"पीड्यमानाः","m":"tormented"},{"d":"विबुधाः","m":"learned"},{"d":"दीप्स्सैः","m":"intense"},{"d":"तपोभिः","m":"austerities also"},{"d":"पितामहम्","m":"Brahma"},{"d":"अपूजयन्","m":"worshipped"}]},{"v":32,"dev":"देवतानांहितार्थायमहात्मावैपितामहः उवाचदेवताःसर्वाइदंतुष्टोमहद्वचः ।","trans":"\"Gratified by the worship of Devatas, wishing them good, Brahma spoke these words.\"","words":[{"d":"तुष्टः","m":"gratified"},{"d":"महात्मा","m":"great self"},{"d":"पितामहः","m":"Brahma"},{"d":"देवतानाम्","m":"to Devatas"},{"d":"हितार्थाय","m":"wishing good"},{"d":"देवताः","m":"Devatas"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"thus"},{"d":"महत्","m":"great"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":33,"dev":"अद्यप्रभृतिलोकांस्त्रीन् सर्वेदानवराक्षसाः भयेनप्रावृतानित्यंविचरिष्यन्तिशाश्वतम् ।","trans":"\"From now ,all Danavas and Rakshasas will range the three worlds every day permanently in fear.\"","words":[{"d":"अद्यप्रभृति","m":"from now"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"नित्यम्","m":"every day"},{"d":"भयेन","m":"in fear"},{"d":"प्रावृताः","m":"range"},{"d":"शाश्वतम्","m":"permanently"},{"d":"त्रीन्","m":"three"},{"d":"लोकान्","m":"worlds"},{"d":"विचरिष्यन्ति","m":"will wander"}]},{"v":34,"dev":"दैवतैस्तुसमागम्यसर्वैश्चेन्द्रपुरोगमैः वृषध्वजस्त्रिपुरहामहादेवःप्रसादितः ।","trans":"\"Getting together all the Devatas marched towards Indra and propitiated Lord MahaDeva, destroyer of Tripura, who Bears the sign of bull on his abode.\"","words":[{"d":"इन्द्रपुरोगमैः","m":"marching towards Indra"},{"d":"सर्वैः","m":"all"},{"d":"दैवतैः","m":"Devatas"},{"d":"समागम्य","m":"getting together"},{"d":"वृषध्वजः","m":"device of bull"},{"d":"त्रिपुरहा","m":"Tripura"},{"d":"महादेवः","m":"Lord MahaDeva"}]},{"v":35,"dev":"प्रसन्नस्तुमहादेवोदेवानेतद्वचोऽब्रवीत् उत्पत्स्यतिहितार्थंवोनारीरक्षःक्षयावहा ।","trans":"MahaDeva was pleased by the Devatas and spoke these words for their benefit,\" a woman will be born for the destruction of Rakshasas.\"","words":[{"d":"प्रसन्नः","m":"pleased"},{"d":"महादेवः","m":"MahaDeva"},{"d":"देवान्","m":"Devatas"},{"d":"एतत्","m":"this"},{"d":"वचः","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"},{"d":"हितार्थम्","m":"their benefit"},{"d":"रक्षःक्षयावहा","m":"for destruction of Rakshasas"},{"d":"नारी","m":"woman"},{"d":"उत्पत्स्यति","m":"will be born"}]},{"v":36,"dev":"एषादेवैःप्रयुक्तातुक्षुद्यथादानवान् पुरा भक्षयिष्यतिनःसीताराक्षसघ्नीसरावणान् ।","trans":"\"Just as hunger consumed Danavas earlier, this woman, instigated (by Devatas) will consume all Rakshasas and Ravana.\"","words":[{"d":"पुरा","m":"earlier"},{"d":"क्षुत्","m":"hunger"},{"d":"दानवान् यथा","m":"Danavas also"},{"d":"देवैः","m":"Devatas"},{"d":"प्रयुक्ताः","m":"instigated"},{"d":"राक्षसघ्नी","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"एषासीता","m":"Sita"},{"d":"सरावणान्","m":"that Ravana"},{"d":"नः","m":"also"},{"d":"भक्षयिष्यति","m":"will consume"}]},{"v":37,"dev":"रावणस्यापनीतेनदुर्विनीतस्यदुर्मतेः अयंनिष्टानकोघोरंशोकेनसमभिप्लुतः ।","trans":"\"Because of the misconduct of the evilminded Ravana's immoral action, terrific destruction attended by grief stares at us.\"","words":[{"d":"दुर्विनीतस्य","m":"misconduct"},{"d":"दुर्मतेः","m":"evil minded"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"अपनीतेन","m":"immoral action"},{"d":"शोकेन","m":"in grief"},{"d":"समभिप्लुतः","m":"attended by"},{"d":"घोरः","m":"terrific"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"us"},{"d":"निष्टानकः","m":"stares at us"}]},{"v":38,"dev":"तंन पश्यामहेलोकेयोनःशरणदोभवेत् राघवेणोपसृष्टानां कालेनेव युगक्षये ।","trans":"\"Threatened like this by Raghava, we cannot perceive anyone in this world who can protect us now. Just as beings are threatened by the time spirit at the end of the destruction of this world, we are threatened.\"","words":[{"d":"युगक्षये","m":"at the time of destruction of the world"},{"d":"उपसृष्टानाम् इव","m":"threatened like this"},{"d":"राघवेण","m":"by Raghava"},{"d":"नः","m":"not"},{"d":"लोके","m":"in this world"},{"d":"शरणदः","m":"can protect"},{"d":"भवेत्","m":"us"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"न पश्यामहे","m":"not able to perceive"}]},{"v":39,"dev":"नास्तिनःशरणंकश्चिद्भयेमहतितिष्ठताम् दावाग्निवेष्टितानांहिकरेणूनांयथावने ।","trans":"\"Indeed, there is no protection for us here to stay, as we are like the female elephants in the forest covered by huge wildfire.\"","words":[{"d":"वने","m":"in the forest"},{"d":"दावाग्निवेष्टितानाम्","m":"like wild fire"},{"d":"करेणूनांयथा","m":"like female elephants"},{"d":"महति","m":"huge"},{"d":"भये","m":"fear"},{"d":"तिष्ठताम्","m":"stays"},{"d":"नः","m":"none"},{"d":"शरणम्","m":"to protect"},{"d":"कश्चित्","m":"indeed"},{"d":"नास्ति","m":"not there"}]},{"v":40,"dev":"प्राप्तकालंकृतंतेनपौलस्त्येनमहात्मना यतएवंभयंदृष्टंतमेवशरणंगतः ।","trans":"\"Great Vibheeshana of the Paulastya race, perceiving opportune time, has sought refuge out of fear.\"","words":[{"d":"महात्मना","m":"great self"},{"d":"तेनपौलस्त्येन","m":"by that Paulastya"},{"d":"प्राप्तकालम्","m":"opportune time having come"},{"d":"कृतम्","m":"did"},{"d":"यतः","m":"that which"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"भयम्","m":"fear"},{"d":"दृष्टम्","m":"perceiving"},{"d":"तमेव","m":"he also"},{"d":"शरणंगतः","m":"sought refuge"}]}]}